<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أخرجه مسلم <span class="c2">(ج٣ ص١٢١٣ - ١٣١٤)</span>.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>